			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				This starts out by asking some dude in the warriors guild in freeport (forgot his name but he's outside somewhere on some grass). say you're looking for work and he'll tell you to go see lady shae at the hogcallers inn. go to the inn, run upsatairs and say to her, i have no house. run back to the inkeep and buy white or red wine. give her the red and she'll talk about a DE giving notes to a halfling in the inn. go to the haflings room and wait till she drops a key. go turn the key into the man who sells the booze and you get a note. return it to the man who you first talked to. he will tell you to go to the arena and give the note to some lady. give it to her and she'll tell you to find opal darkbringer and the halfling and put their heads in this bag and bring em to me.  So i killed the halfling, got her head and now im stuck with opal darkbriar. i went in East Freeport and found out that there are 2 opal darkbriars. i need to kill the DE i believe but she is wayyy to hard with all those other trainers around her. any clues on how to get her head?
				</font>
